T1  - An Approach to Solving Multiple Criteria Macroeconomic Policy Problems and an Application
AU  - Wallenius, Hannele
AU  - Wallenius, Jyrki
AU  - Vartia, Pentti
Y1  - 1978/06/01
PY  - 1978
DA  - 1978/06/01
